1
00:00:00,810 --> 00:00:01,810
(Episode 75)

2
00:00:01,810 --> 00:00:03,580
Why don't you just answer my question?

3
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:06,540
It's not something I want to discuss.

4
00:00:07,250 --> 00:00:09,310
And it certainly can't be made public.

5
00:00:09,650 --> 00:00:11,780
Stop playing word games and answer me.

6
00:00:13,950 --> 00:00:15,450
If you're really my mother,

7
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:19,190
then tell me why you're trying to marry me
to Ma Seo Rin.

8
00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:20,630
What?

9
00:00:21,030 --> 00:00:24,360
Wait, so Kang Jun Ho is
Chae Hwa Young's son?

10
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:28,870
Not now. I'll explain it all later.

11
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:32,740
What is certain is that you're my son,

12
00:00:33,440 --> 00:00:35,970
and Seo Rin is not my biological daughter.

13
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:38,110
The child in that photo...

14
00:00:38,940 --> 00:00:40,080
was Kang Jun Ho.

15
00:00:43,150 --> 00:00:44,580
That's absolute nonsense.

16
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:47,320
I don't need to hear another word.

17
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:50,560
Jun Ho, sit down.
Your mother has something to say. Please.

18
00:00:50,620 --> 00:00:52,220
Don't you dare call yourself my mother.

19
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:57,830
I have no desire at all to be your son,
so stop it!

20
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:00,530
Please, just listen to me.

21
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:03,270
There are too many eyes on me.

22
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:07,270
I couldn't publicly acknowledge you
as my son.

23
00:01:07,570 --> 00:01:08,640
But I would...

24
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:11,980
do anything
to ensure you inherit Dream Group.

25
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:13,080
Says who?

26
00:01:13,310 --> 00:01:14,380
Dream Group...

27
00:01:15,180 --> 00:01:18,420
My final duty as your mother is
to make sure you inherit this kingdom.

28
00:01:18,780 --> 00:01:19,980
And that's why...

29
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,420
you tried to make her marry me?

30
00:01:25,860 --> 00:01:27,630
In the end, just to get what you wanted,

31
00:01:28,730 --> 00:01:30,260
you only came looking for the son
you abandoned.

32
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,700
That's not true.
Please, don't misunderstand.

33
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:38,100
I wanted to give it to you.
Only to you, my son.

34
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:43,170
I waited until I had enough power
to come back for you.

35
00:01:44,140 --> 00:01:46,680
All so I could give Dream Group to my son.

36
00:01:47,210 --> 00:01:50,350
I lived for that day and that day alone.

37
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:55,520
I thought it was the only way
I could atone for what I did to you.

38
00:01:56,450 --> 00:01:58,960
Please, believe me.
Trust your mother. Please.

39
00:02:00,690 --> 00:02:02,090
We're so close now.

40
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:06,330
That's why
I'm trying to have you marry Seo Rin.

41
00:02:07,670 --> 00:02:10,270
When I have you, my own son,
my own flesh and blood,

42
00:02:10,970 --> 00:02:13,810
why would I ever want to give Dream Group
to a total stranger like Seo Rin?

43
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:18,580
We'll join forces, you and I,
and take Dream for ourselves.

44
00:02:19,610 --> 00:02:21,710
That dream is within our reach.

45
00:02:23,580 --> 00:02:24,580
Get out.

46
00:02:26,450 --> 00:02:27,450
I said, get out.

47
00:02:29,950 --> 00:02:34,260
- I'm done being played by your lies.
- Jun Ho...

48
00:02:35,690 --> 00:02:36,830
When the time is right...

49
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:40,800
I'll tell you everything about
how I ended up raising Seo Rin.

50
00:02:41,570 --> 00:02:42,570
But for now,

51
00:02:43,570 --> 00:02:44,840
please, just trust your mother.

52
00:03:00,890 --> 00:03:04,120
Chae Hwa Young.
Is there no end to your wickedness?

53
00:03:04,720 --> 00:03:06,590
The more I dig, the more secrets I find.

54
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:09,290
So you even abandoned Jun Ho
when he was just a baby?

55
00:03:09,990 --> 00:03:12,000
And on top of that, you stole Seo Rin,
who's a twin.

56
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:14,600
I'm speechless.

57
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,940
That's why
I'm trying to have you marry Seo Rin.

58
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:21,270
When I have you, my own son,
my own flesh and blood,

59
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:24,510
why would I ever want to give Dream Group
to a total stranger like Seo Rin?

60
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:27,710
We'll join forces, you and I,
and take Dream for ourselves.

61
00:03:32,550 --> 00:03:34,890
This child is General Manager Kang Jun Ho?

62
00:03:36,420 --> 00:03:37,460
No way.

63
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,620
Does that mean General Manager Kang
was adopted?

64
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:42,590
Baek Ho didn't seem to have any idea.

65
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:44,460
What should I do?

66
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:49,370
(General Manager Kang Jun Ho)

67
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:58,610
Seo Rin isn't CEO Chae's daughter?

68
00:04:20,300 --> 00:04:21,300
CEO Chae.

69
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,500
Is something wrong?

70
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,970
I told Jun Ho.

71
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:28,140
That I'm...

72
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,840
That I'm...

73
00:04:31,110 --> 00:04:32,410
That you're his mother?

74
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:35,780
Yes.

75
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,880
In the long run,
it's better that he knows.

76
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:42,750
So...

77
00:04:43,620 --> 00:04:44,690
who is his father?

78
00:04:46,890 --> 00:04:49,160
- What?
- I'm asking about Jun Ho's father.

79
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,630
Who is Jun Ho's biological father?

80
00:04:52,060 --> 00:04:53,560
Why are you asking me that?

81
00:04:54,470 --> 00:04:57,300
He has nothing to do with you.
Jun Ho is my son, and mine alone.

82
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:02,970
I'm tired. Get out.

83
00:05:05,210 --> 00:05:07,010
Then I'll do some digging
and find out myself...

84
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:10,850
who Jun Ho's real father is.

85
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:29,000
Hey, we're running low on vegetables.
Can you restock them?

86
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:30,270
Okay.

87
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:31,770
(Bomdama)

88
00:05:31,900 --> 00:05:35,470
Individual pots are convenient, right?
You can just pick whatever you like.

89
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:38,380
I was actually worried since Mom and Bo Ra
have such different tastes,

90
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:42,110
but this is much neater
since everyone can add what they want.

91
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,250
We might need to make a reservation
next time.

92
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:45,950
This place is really packed.

93
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:48,820
If business stays like this,
I couldn't ask for anything more.

94
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:51,760
I told Jang Mi to stop by for a bite
since she likes shabu-shabu too.

95
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:54,690
That's great.
I was hoping to see her anyway.

96
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:59,260
I gave Jang Mi some acorn jelly.
She loves it.

97
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:00,870
Mom, hush.

98
00:06:01,570 --> 00:06:05,140
- She knows about it too? She saw Jang Mi?
- Yes, I saw Jang Mi.

99
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,470
I miss Jang Mi.

100
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:12,280
Grandma, hush.
We shouldn't be so loud in public.

101
00:06:12,410 --> 00:06:14,050
My preschool teacher told me.

102
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:16,780
That's right, Bo Ra.
You're such a good girl.

103
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,720
Bo Ra, would you like more meat?

104
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:21,550
- Yes.
- Okay, enjoy your meal.

105
00:06:21,850 --> 00:06:23,190
Okay, I'll get it for you right now.

106
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:32,430
What's the status of the registration
for Dream Resort?

107
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,870
We've finalized our coordination
with the environmental groups.

108
00:06:35,630 --> 00:06:38,070
We presented a mutually beneficial plan
for developers and environmental groups.

109
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:40,340
We've also prevented problems...

110
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:43,110
- like deforestation and river pollution.
- Right.

111
00:06:43,510 --> 00:06:46,740
We will also create alternative habitats
for the local flora and fauna,

112
00:06:46,980 --> 00:06:48,780
and designate certain areas
for conservation.

113
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:53,890
The environmental impact assessment
was approved, so there are no issues.

114
00:06:54,250 --> 00:06:55,490
Yes. I'll take my leave now.

115
00:06:56,650 --> 00:06:57,660
Wait.

116
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:01,030
Where is Oh Jang Mi?

117
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:06,860
You two seem to enjoy ganging up on me
and causing trouble.

118
00:07:07,300 --> 00:07:10,100
I guess you think this company
is your personal playground.

119
00:07:10,370 --> 00:07:11,370
More importantly,

120
00:07:12,640 --> 00:07:13,840
now that Ms. Oh Jang Mi is awake,

121
00:07:14,370 --> 00:07:16,170
aren't you curious
what she's saying about you?

122
00:07:16,470 --> 00:07:17,680
Isn't that what's really bothering you?

123
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,650
Shut up.

124
00:07:21,650 --> 00:07:23,010
Just tell me where Oh Jang Mi is.

125
00:07:23,350 --> 00:07:24,880
You think ordering me to talk
is going to work?

126
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:27,050
Why waste your breath asking?

127
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:31,290
Find her yourself, CEO Chae.
You're the expert at tailing people.

128
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:35,230
- What did you just say, Kang Baek Ho?
- What exactly do you expect me to say?

129
00:07:35,990 --> 00:07:39,200
I know enough about you to be a problem,
so you'd better watch yourself.

130
00:07:39,660 --> 00:07:40,730
If you push me too far,

131
00:07:41,030 --> 00:07:43,430
I won't hesitate to expose the truth
about the twins.

132
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:52,540
Everyone's threatening me about the twins.

133
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,310
Kang Baek Ho.

134
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:57,320
You really think I can't find Oh Jang Mi
just because you've hidden her?

135
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,520
I'm sure you are busy, Oh Jang Mi.

136
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,560
Mom?

137
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:15,670
Who's Oh Jang Mi?

138
00:08:18,270 --> 00:08:19,270
Wait...

139
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:22,640
Could Oh Jang Mi be pretending
to be Seo Rin?

140
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:26,710
But with the glasses on,
she was definitely Oh Jang Mi.

141
00:08:48,070 --> 00:08:49,370
Colored contacts?

142
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:51,140
And they're prescription.

143
00:08:51,870 --> 00:08:53,500
But she had laser eye surgery.

144
00:08:54,370 --> 00:08:56,110
Why would Seo Rin wear these?

145
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:58,640
She's was even wearing glasses earlier.

146
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:04,780
Why is CEO Chae here at this hour?

147
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:16,190
Director. How have you been?

148
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:17,930
I hope you've been well.

149
00:09:18,430 --> 00:09:23,230
It's been a while since Seo Rin's surgery,
and I've yet to treat you to a meal.

150
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:28,110
Do you have time for a quick cup of tea?

151
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:30,040
There's something I'd like to ask you.

152
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:33,240
(Korea University Hospital)

153
00:09:33,710 --> 00:09:38,180
As you know, you're the one
who performed Seo Rin's LASEK surgery.

154
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,520
Yes, that's right.

155
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:42,620
I've noticed she's been wearing
contact lenses recently.

156
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:44,820
And sometimes glasses, too.

157
00:09:45,090 --> 00:09:48,630
A lot of people wear cosmetic lenses
or glasses for fashion these days.

158
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:50,800
They don't always wear them because
their vision is bad.

159
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,800
I considered that, but...

160
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:57,270
Is it possible
her vision has gotten worse?

161
00:09:57,500 --> 00:10:00,170
Yes. Even after LASEK,
if myopic regression occurs,

162
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,740
it's possible for vision to worsen.

163
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:06,080
But I'm worried because her eyesight seems
to be even worse since the surgery.

164
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:07,240
Is that even possible?

165
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:10,510
She's too young for vision loss from age,
so I doubt it would be that severe.

166
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:12,280
Unless there's a serious
underlying eye condition.

167
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:14,220
I see.

168
00:10:16,950 --> 00:10:20,360
In that case, I'll bring Seo Rin in
for an eye exam tomorrow.

169
00:10:20,660 --> 00:10:21,730
Yes, please do.

170
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,360
I'll schedule an appointment for you.

171
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:30,840
(Director Ma Seo Rin)

172
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:31,940
Oh my.

173
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:39,380
Stop that. You'll scratch your eye.

174
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,480
I'm fine.

175
00:10:45,920 --> 00:10:48,950
Don't you have any eye drops?
Here, let me put them in for you.

176
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:52,120
You're offering to do it for me?

177
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:54,260
No, that's all right.

178
00:10:58,500 --> 00:11:00,600
Teaming up with Chae Hwa Young
to take over Dream?

179
00:11:01,170 --> 00:11:05,240
Fat chance. I'll never let that happen.

180
00:11:15,950 --> 00:11:20,350
- CEO Chae came by earlier. Not sure why.
- She did?

181
00:11:21,220 --> 00:11:24,890
- Ma'am, you're not going to believe this.
- What is it?

182
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:28,460
CEO Chae has a biological son.
And do you know who it is?

183
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,560
Who?

184
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:34,000
General Manager Kang Jun Ho.
Baek Ho's brother.

185
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:35,530
My gosh.

186
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:39,400
So that's why she invited him over
and made such a scene last time.

187
00:11:42,310 --> 00:11:46,010
Chae Hwa Young is out for blood,
so you need to be careful.

188
00:11:46,310 --> 00:11:47,310
Okay.

189
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:50,510
Baek Ho...

190
00:11:50,820 --> 00:11:54,490
- Yes?
- I shouldn't bring up Jun Ho, should I?

191
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:56,250
Come on.

192
00:11:56,920 --> 00:11:58,590
You're about to tell me you love me,
aren't you?

193
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:00,120
I know, I know.

194
00:12:00,520 --> 00:12:03,630
I could hear it a thousand times
and never get tired of it, so go ahead.

195
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:10,370
You were on the phone?

196
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:11,870
I need to go.

197
00:12:13,770 --> 00:12:14,970
Mom, what's up?

198
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:17,410
You're coming with me
to the eye doctor tomorrow.

199
00:12:17,740 --> 00:12:18,740
The eye doctor?

200
00:12:18,810 --> 00:12:21,950
We need to get your LASEK surgery
checked out.

201
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:24,780
A check-up? Why all of a sudden?

202
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:28,520
I saw you in contacts, and you've started
wearing glasses when you never did before.

203
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:30,520
It makes me worry.

204
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:35,890
They're just blue light glasses
because I'm staring at a screen all day.

205
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:39,030
- Don't worry, Mom.
- It's been ten years since your surgery.

206
00:12:39,330 --> 00:12:42,270
It's checkup time, so clear your schedule
for tomorrow morning.

207
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:43,800
I made an appointment for ten.

208
00:12:50,670 --> 00:12:51,680
What am I going to do?

209
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,580
This is sweet.

210
00:12:54,010 --> 00:12:55,510
- Slow down.
- You really have to try this.

211
00:12:55,580 --> 00:12:58,080
- I'm home.
- Hey.

212
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,050
My, Jun Ho.

213
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:02,150
Have you been drinking?

214
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:03,920
No, Mom, I...

215
00:13:04,020 --> 00:13:05,560
I can smell it on you.

216
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,060
Did something happen?

217
00:13:08,430 --> 00:13:11,700
Son, what's wrong? You don't even drink.

218
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:13,060
Seriously, Jun Ho.

219
00:13:13,930 --> 00:13:16,170
I'm sorry for interrupting...

220
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:18,570
your nice, quiet family moment.

221
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:21,710
Hey, Jun Ho.

222
00:13:23,470 --> 00:13:24,640
Come talk to me for a second.

223
00:13:32,550 --> 00:13:34,290
Why'd you drink so much?

224
00:13:35,090 --> 00:13:36,150
What's wrong?

225
00:13:36,850 --> 00:13:37,890
Is it...

226
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:40,060
because of Director Ma Seo Rin?

227
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:41,790
Because she said she likes me?

228
00:13:43,060 --> 00:13:44,330
Must be nice for you.

229
00:13:50,100 --> 00:13:52,200
Mom and Dad are really great people.

230
00:13:53,070 --> 00:13:54,100
Aren't they?

231
00:14:04,620 --> 00:14:05,820
What the heck is wrong with him?

232
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:10,020
No matter how I look at it,
that's got to be Seo Rin.

233
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,220
No doubt about it. Right, Mom?

234
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:16,960
Plus, the way CEO Chae threatened you
to keep your mouth shut.

235
00:14:17,490 --> 00:14:19,500
It has to mean there's a secret
about them being twins.

236
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,630
A secret about the twins?

237
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:24,240
That makes sense.

238
00:14:24,900 --> 00:14:27,400
If they're just look-alikes,
like Tae Pyung said,

239
00:14:27,770 --> 00:14:29,110
and they just happen
to have different mothers,

240
00:14:29,510 --> 00:14:33,010
why would Chae Hwa Young go so far as
to take that awful photo to threaten me?

241
00:14:33,980 --> 00:14:38,580
It's because there's a huge secret
that she needs to shut me up about.

242
00:14:38,680 --> 00:14:39,750
Exactly.

243
00:14:40,450 --> 00:14:42,890
Mom, if we play our cards right,
this could be huge.

244
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:45,490
We might finally have
some real leverage over CEO Chae.

245
00:14:45,860 --> 00:14:46,860
Right?

246
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:49,490
Gosh, to think I begged
on my knees for nothing.

247
00:14:50,430 --> 00:14:52,900
Anyway, let's keep our eyes peeled...

248
00:14:53,030 --> 00:14:55,630
and watch every single move
that Chae Hwa Young makes.

249
00:14:55,900 --> 00:14:59,100
If we do, we're bound to find something
we can use against her.

250
00:15:05,180 --> 00:15:06,210
Is that so?

251
00:15:08,050 --> 00:15:09,480
So that's what happened?

252
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,450
The eye doctor tomorrow?

253
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:15,720
Yes.

254
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:21,790
Do you happen to know which clinic
Seo Rin got LASEK at ten years ago?

255
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:23,830
Ten years ago?

256
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:26,400
I'm not sure.

257
00:15:27,670 --> 00:15:30,530
This is a disaster.
I haven't even had LASEK.

258
00:15:30,730 --> 00:15:34,540
If I go for an exam, they'll find out
I'm not Seo Rin in a heartbeat.

259
00:15:35,070 --> 00:15:36,440
That is a problem.

260
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:41,280
Do you think Chae Hwa Young is suspicious
and this is some kind of test?

261
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:43,450
Then you'll be caught red-handed.

262
00:15:43,450 --> 00:15:46,080
Geum Soon, please try to remember.

263
00:15:46,350 --> 00:15:49,220
We have to find out
which clinic it was right now!

264
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:54,390
Maybe it's the same eye clinic
the Chairman and CEO Chae go to?

265
00:15:55,290 --> 00:15:57,190
They're close with Dr. Kim there.

266
00:15:57,930 --> 00:15:59,730
Yes! I'll give it a shot.

267
00:16:01,530 --> 00:16:03,930
I don't know
what I would've done without you.

268
00:16:03,930 --> 00:16:04,940
Geum Soon. Thank you so much.

269
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:11,480
Oh, dear.
What is she getting herself into?

270
00:16:12,140 --> 00:16:14,180
I hope she can get through this
without getting caught.

271
00:16:16,250 --> 00:16:17,680
Get through what unscathed?

272
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:24,860
Getting through each day safely
is a blessing in itself.

273
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:29,190
Geum Soon.

274
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:33,100
You seem to have gotten
awfully close with Seo Rin lately.

275
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:34,330
What?

276
00:16:34,730 --> 00:16:36,570
Oh my goodness,
what are you talking about?

277
00:16:37,100 --> 00:16:39,370
How could I possibly be
close with Seo Rin?

278
00:16:40,070 --> 00:16:42,870
You're just saying that
to try and get me fired.

279
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:44,910
Fine, if you say so.

280
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:52,220
I should get Hwa Young
a bouquet of flowers tomorrow.

281
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:56,490
After what I said the other day,
she must be upset with me.

282
00:16:56,820 --> 00:16:59,590
It's CEO Chae.
I wonder what this is about.

283
00:17:03,730 --> 00:17:05,000
Yes, CEO Chae.

284
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:08,030
Lawyer Han, how have you been?

285
00:17:08,800 --> 00:17:13,240
- I hope I'm not disturbing you this late.
- Not at all. It's fine.

286
00:17:13,570 --> 00:17:18,280
Actually, I was just wondering
why I hadn't heard from you.

287
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,240
You were?

288
00:17:21,450 --> 00:17:24,050
Usually, it's up to the parents
to move things along with the wedding,

289
00:17:24,480 --> 00:17:26,550
but I've been so busy
after just bringing it up,

290
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:28,520
and I've let all this time pass.

291
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:30,050
I do apologize.

292
00:17:30,320 --> 00:17:31,520
Please, don't apologize.

293
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:36,130
It seemed like our Jun Ho was
having a hard time making up his mind,

294
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:38,560
so I didn't press the issue.

295
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:43,000
So, does this mean
Jun Ho has made up his mind?

296
00:17:43,870 --> 00:17:45,000
I suppose so.

297
00:17:46,070 --> 00:17:49,410
In fact, he came home after having
some drinks tonight, which he rarely does.

298
00:17:49,470 --> 00:17:52,110
Apparently, he was rambling
to his younger sibling.

299
00:17:52,910 --> 00:17:56,080
I suppose now that he's
actually facing marriage,

300
00:17:56,810 --> 00:18:00,020
- he must have a lot on his mind.
- What? He was drinking?

301
00:18:00,620 --> 00:18:02,620
Not a lot. Just a little.

302
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:08,260
Anyway, let's agree to
move forward with their wedding.

303
00:18:08,690 --> 00:18:12,130
Yes, then I'll arrange a time
to see you, Lawyer Han.

304
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:14,130
And let's keep in touch.

305
00:18:14,470 --> 00:18:16,030
Yes, goodbye.

306
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:23,040
Was that about the kids' wedding?

307
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:24,340
Yes.

308
00:18:25,540 --> 00:18:27,340
I was wondering what the holdup was,

309
00:18:27,950 --> 00:18:31,620
and CEO Chae said she's just been
too busy to move things along.

310
00:18:32,920 --> 00:18:36,120
With that whole power abuse scandal,
I was feeling a little uneasy,

311
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:38,460
but from the way she was talking,

312
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:41,020
she doesn't seem like
such a terrible person after all.

313
00:18:41,330 --> 00:18:45,200
That scandal was a smear campaign
against CEO Chae.

314
00:18:45,660 --> 00:18:49,300
Anyway, that aside,
when it comes to Jun Ho's marriage,

315
00:18:49,870 --> 00:18:54,270
we need to be more cautious.
I'm not on board with it.

316
00:18:55,710 --> 00:18:58,440
Still, I wonder what's going on
with our Jun Ho.

317
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:01,410
He seems to be really struggling.

318
00:19:03,910 --> 00:19:05,850
Could it be about the marriage
to my daughter?

319
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:19,600
Seo Rin.

320
00:19:20,060 --> 00:19:23,100
You said acorn jelly was too mushy.
What's gotten into you?

321
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:25,940
What?

322
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:27,940
Have your tastes changed all of a sudden?

323
00:19:32,010 --> 00:19:34,210
I guess my taste buds are
taking after Grandfather's.

324
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:36,310
Now that I'm trying it,
I actually like it.

325
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:47,520
What? You got something to say to me?

326
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:50,360
Something to say? Of course not.

327
00:19:50,890 --> 00:19:53,960
I'm just worried about your health, dear.

328
00:19:56,700 --> 00:20:01,100
Because of your high blood pressure,
Dr. Kim said we must avoid any shocks.

329
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:03,470
He really stressed that point,
you haven't forgotten, have you?

330
00:20:04,980 --> 00:20:07,280
You have to stay healthy, no matter what.

331
00:20:07,580 --> 00:20:11,320
It's the only way
our Hong Ju and I can survive.

332
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:13,450
Making it sound like he's on his deathbed.

333
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:18,260
Seo Rin, hurry up and finish eating.
You have an eye appointment at ten.

334
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,960
Right.

335
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:26,200
(Korea University Hospital)

336
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:28,230
(Director's Office)

337
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:43,910
Come on in. You too, Seo Rin.

338
00:20:44,080 --> 00:20:46,880
I'm fine, but my mom is overreacting.

339
00:20:47,520 --> 00:20:49,090
We're here for your own good.

340
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:51,120
Let's get the examination started.

341
00:20:51,420 --> 00:20:53,790
Seeing you in glasses
even after your LASEK surgery,

342
00:20:53,860 --> 00:20:55,690
your mom must have been really worried.

343
00:20:56,190 --> 00:20:58,500
All right, let's test your vision again,
shall we?

344
00:21:00,430 --> 00:21:01,570
But I'm fine.

345
00:21:07,500 --> 00:21:08,670
Please have a seat right here.

346
00:21:31,560 --> 00:21:33,000
Okay, and this one?

347
00:21:36,830 --> 00:21:37,970
Just a second.

348
00:21:39,100 --> 00:21:43,470
All right, Oh Jang Mi. You're so busted.
I know you're Oh Jang Mi.

349
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,680
Two.

350
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:53,420
Three.

351
00:21:54,380 --> 00:21:55,390
Five.

352
00:21:56,650 --> 00:21:57,650
Two.

353
00:21:58,690 --> 00:22:01,290
- Four.
- Okay, now the other eye.

354
00:22:04,290 --> 00:22:05,300
G.

355
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:07,300
Two.

356
00:22:08,600 --> 00:22:09,600
Six.

357
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:11,400
Seven.

358
00:22:12,370 --> 00:22:13,370
Six.

359
00:22:14,710 --> 00:22:15,770
You did great.

360
00:22:19,110 --> 00:22:20,440
Could she really be Seo Rin?

361
00:22:21,650 --> 00:22:23,480
Maybe I'm just being paranoid.

362
00:22:24,820 --> 00:22:26,250
There's nothing seriously wrong, CEO Chae.

363
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:30,690
She said her vision was getting worse.
Is she okay?

364
00:22:31,490 --> 00:22:33,590
Yes, it hasn't gotten significantly worse.

365
00:22:33,920 --> 00:22:36,230
It's just fluctuating
within the normal range.

366
00:22:37,260 --> 00:22:38,530
I told you, Mom.

367
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:41,900
It's fine to wear contacts or glasses,
but you always make such a fuss.

368
00:22:42,830 --> 00:22:45,270
I just wish my eyes weren't so dry.

369
00:22:45,600 --> 00:22:47,670
LASEK surgery does tend
to make your eyes a bit dry.

370
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:50,110
You'll be fine
if you use artificial tears sometimes.

371
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:53,080
I'm just glad to hear everything's okay.

372
00:22:59,850 --> 00:23:04,320
Mom, I told you I'm fine.
This was all for nothing, a waste of time.

373
00:23:04,490 --> 00:23:06,690
Still, it's good to be sure.
Don't be like that.

374
00:23:08,330 --> 00:23:11,030
I'll run errands, then head to the office.
You can go on ahead, Mom.

375
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:14,970
- Where are you going?
- To the mall. I need some retail therapy.

376
00:23:15,270 --> 00:23:18,700
She was lying low for a while,
but that old habit is back again.

377
00:23:19,540 --> 00:23:20,540
I'm off.

378
00:23:29,850 --> 00:23:30,850
Director.

379
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,580
Thank you.

380
00:23:33,150 --> 00:23:35,520
My mom just tends to overreact.

381
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:39,290
I memorized the chart like you told me,
and everything went smoothly.

382
00:23:39,490 --> 00:23:43,460
Still, I feel uneasy
about deceiving CEO Chae.

383
00:23:43,690 --> 00:23:47,600
Come on, Director.
You promised you'd keep it a secret.

384
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:50,530
I'm so glad I took care
of this in advance.

385
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:56,910
Director,
By any chance, has my mom contacted you?

386
00:23:57,110 --> 00:23:59,210
Yes, I just saw her a little while ago.

387
00:23:59,780 --> 00:24:01,180
She said your eyesight
has been getting worse,

388
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:04,480
and she was worried because she thinks
you've been wearing glasses and contacts.

389
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,920
She made an appointment
for ten in the morning tomorrow.

390
00:24:07,250 --> 00:24:08,990
Gosh, she's making such a fuss.

391
00:24:08,990 --> 00:24:11,760
Director, could you please
send me the eye chart?

392
00:24:11,990 --> 00:24:13,760
I'll memorize it for the exam.

393
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:16,430
Is there a reason you have to go that far?

394
00:24:16,590 --> 00:24:20,600
She keeps saying my eyes are getting worse
because I'm on my phone all night,

395
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:24,670
and she's been nagging me nonstop.
I don't want to fight over little things.

396
00:24:24,900 --> 00:24:26,940
Please, just help me out, Director. Okay?

397
00:24:28,910 --> 00:24:32,280
Thanks to you, Director, I was able to
get through it without getting caught.

398
00:24:32,710 --> 00:24:33,810
Thank you, Director.

399
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:37,050
Come by again soon.

400
00:24:54,100 --> 00:24:55,400
So you're telling me that Seo Rin...

401
00:24:55,970 --> 00:24:59,240
asked you to hide the fact that
she never had LASEK surgery?

402
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:02,470
Yes. The truth is, doctors can tell.

403
00:25:03,440 --> 00:25:06,380
You see, every person
has a different iris.

404
00:25:07,610 --> 00:25:10,650
Furthermore, Seo Rin had LASEK surgery,

405
00:25:11,050 --> 00:25:13,050
but the young woman
who came with you today...

406
00:25:14,150 --> 00:25:16,790
had no signs of having had
LASEK surgery at all.

407
00:25:17,290 --> 00:25:20,520
I had a gut feeling right then
that she wasn't Ma Seo Rin,

408
00:25:21,290 --> 00:25:23,460
but I figured it must be
some kind of family matter.

409
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:28,570
Oh Jang Mi. That audacious little brat
was fooling me this whole time?

410
00:25:29,700 --> 00:25:32,570
To think this was happening
right under my nose, in my own home.

411
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:36,810
But she looks exactly like Seo Rin.

412
00:25:37,770 --> 00:25:40,880
- Who is she then?
- You don't need to know.

413
00:25:41,280 --> 00:25:42,750
Please keep this strictly confidential.

414
00:25:43,410 --> 00:25:45,350
I'll make it well worth your while.

415
00:25:51,050 --> 00:25:52,090
What did you just say?

416
00:25:52,690 --> 00:25:54,720
The Seo Rin living at your house
was actually Oh Jang Mi?

417
00:25:56,130 --> 00:25:59,430
- Unbelievable.
- I know, right? It's jaw-dropping.

418
00:26:00,330 --> 00:26:02,700
I was absolutely flabbergasted.

419
00:26:03,330 --> 00:26:05,800
I'm telling you, she's the most
audacious brat I have ever met.

420
00:26:06,500 --> 00:26:09,910
Did Oh Jang Mi really think
I wouldn't notice her posing as Seo Rin?

421
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:14,310
No wonder. I had a feeling
she had you all figured out, CEO Chae.

422
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:16,080
That brat, Oh Jang Mi...

423
00:26:16,350 --> 00:26:19,650
was right beside me all this time,
tricking me as Ma Seo Rin.

424
00:26:20,580 --> 00:26:23,090
She must have felt so smug all this time,
Oh Jang Mi.

425
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,890
- Oh my, it's hot!
- It's hot!

426
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:27,720
Oh no, what do we do?

427
00:26:30,060 --> 00:26:31,430
My legs...

428
00:26:32,230 --> 00:26:33,430
I'm freezing.

429
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:38,340
Oh my gosh!

430
00:26:38,340 --> 00:26:41,940
Seo Rin? Why did you put me through this?

431
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:44,610
What on earth have you been doing?

432
00:26:50,810 --> 00:26:52,220
You shameless creature.

433
00:26:52,550 --> 00:26:54,880
Are you that scared the Chairman
will find out your true colors?

434
00:26:54,950 --> 00:26:56,090
Let go of me!

435
00:26:58,720 --> 00:27:01,890
She must have had a blast
watching me fall for it without a clue.

436
00:27:03,660 --> 00:27:04,890
All right, fine.

437
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:08,900
If that's how Oh Jang Mi wants to play it,
then I'll play along.

438
00:27:10,100 --> 00:27:14,400
- Play along?
- Yes. But first, I'll get Jun Ho married.

439
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:15,710
As soon as possible.

440
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:17,140
But, CEO Chae.

441
00:27:17,710 --> 00:27:20,480
Why do you think Oh Jang Mi
isn't telling the Chairman the truth?

442
00:27:20,680 --> 00:27:22,980
Why else? It's about the money.

443
00:27:23,510 --> 00:27:26,020
- Money?
- Think about how she's lived her life.

444
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:28,120
The daughter of some side dish shop owner,

445
00:27:28,650 --> 00:27:30,820
after living her whole life
as pathetic, poor Oh Jang Mi,

446
00:27:31,520 --> 00:27:35,460
now that she's tasted life as Ma Seo Rin,
you think she's going to give it up?

447
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:40,400
The Chairman gave her a building.
Her title is Dream Group's granddaughter,

448
00:27:41,100 --> 00:27:42,370
and when that old man dies,

449
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:45,700
she thinks the entire family fortune
will be hers.

450
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:47,740
Kang Baek Ho and Oh Tae Pyung.

451
00:27:49,170 --> 00:27:50,610
They must all be in on it together, then.

452
00:27:50,910 --> 00:27:52,410
That's all the more reason to hurry.

453
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:56,980
When I get them married, I'll have
control, both legally and officially.

454
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:01,950
While Oh Jang Mi is busy
pretending to be Ma Seo Rin,

455
00:28:02,420 --> 00:28:05,060
I'm going to act like a real mother
to Ma Seo Rin.

456
00:28:05,590 --> 00:28:08,760
And when I make my move,
I'll finish it all at once.

457
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:11,530
You know what I mean, don't you?

458
00:28:12,330 --> 00:28:13,360
Understood.

459
00:28:19,740 --> 00:28:21,840
I've poured my entire life
into getting this far.

460
00:28:22,870 --> 00:28:24,610
There's no way I'm letting them
take it from me.

461
00:28:25,480 --> 00:28:28,310
Oh Jang Mi. You'd better be ready.

462
00:28:29,650 --> 00:28:32,450
Because I am going to stomp you
into the ground.

463
00:28:53,570 --> 00:28:55,110
(The First Man)

464
00:28:55,170 --> 00:28:58,140
You and your mom go
and bring Jung Suk Hee here now.

465
00:28:58,240 --> 00:29:00,780
I said bring Jung Suk Hee here
without anyone in that house finding out.

466
00:29:01,010 --> 00:29:03,380
Yes, I finally found it!
Chae Hwa Young's safe.

467
00:29:03,450 --> 00:29:06,480
- This is it. The dashcam's memory card.
- Don't tell me this is...

468
00:29:06,550 --> 00:29:07,980
This is my dad's cell phone.

469
00:29:08,450 --> 00:29:11,620
How can this be? It's gone.
Oh Bok Gil's phone is missing,

470
00:29:11,690 --> 00:29:13,390
and so is the memory card. It's gone!

471
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:15,890
They must've gone to the police.
I'm sure they went straight there.

472
00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:17,160
Oh my gosh, Kang Hyuk,
what am I going to do?

473
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:21,560
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
